{
  "stem": "25423.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The final was the director of the gymnasium which I attended, and his wife, and many other people I don't really recall.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very well.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Much better than people here in New York, despite all these extraordinary pressures.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Furthermore, they were clean.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't run that around in jeans and look like refugees, like people in New York.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, under the circumstances, still maintained human dignity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't attend, but I'm aware.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But why did people get married?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A sister of my friend, a very beautiful girl, much older-- slightly older than I, two or three years, married a Jewish policeman because, by marrying him, she was taken out of the [NON-ENGLISH], probably for three or four weeks.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Forget about it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not in Lwow, because--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They buried him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The cemetery.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, they had Jewish cemeteries.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, you ask questions about expressions of normal community life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These are abnormal circumstances, and all I can tell you is, in order to put it in a proper perspective, try to imagine a pressure cooker with heat constantly increased, and people lived, literally, by the hour.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is a very complicated and a very delicate question.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the Jewish police and its command, there were some very decent people who tried their best to help, and alleviate the suffering.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, don't forget that they were created as a mechanism to keep order in the community, keep it quiet and docile.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Eventually, their job was to identify where Jews live, and make it possible for the Germans to collect them in places where they were sent to the death camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I had no experience because, you see, I moved my own way.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
